                      PROCMETER V3.0
                      ==============

A system monitoring program for Linux.


Usage: procmeter3 [-h] ...

-h              Print out a help message.
...             Options, use 'procmeter3 -h' to list them.



Installation
------------

Edit the Makefile to set the paths for installation (INSTDIR), the X Windows
directory (XINCLUDE,XLIBRARY) and the compiler options (CC,LD,CFLAGS).

make all
make install

The manual pages procmeter(3) and procmeterrc(5) gives more details on how to
use the program.


